The paper deals with ontology module extraction, which is a problem in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and logic (cs.LO). The proposed approach involves reasoning in datalog, which is a database query language, making it relevant to databases (cs.DB) and software engineering (cs.SE). Additionally, the paper mentions the ability to tailor the approach to preserve specific kinds of entailments, which could involve programming language concepts (cs.PL).
